<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Frankfurt am Main</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache wegen Verlängerung des Waffenstillstands zwischen der Stadt Nürnberg und den Herren von Hanau.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_335" id="167r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_335_r1l18"><expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_335_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> Als <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw / vnd vns yecʒunden ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l21">gütlıch ſteen ıſt / das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_335_r1l20">nu </ab></add> auf ſant Mıchels tag awſgeet / . <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erſam </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l22"><expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> cʒemal fleiſʒiklıch / daʒ Jr es durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvıllen tün vnd <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l23">gemüwet ſein wollet / vnd beſehen ob Jr mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw <expan>awſgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l24">möcht / daʒ das etlich cʒeite hinfür erlengt würd / . vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> laſſ </del> wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l25">ew das <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein / Als etc vnd das in <expan>ſölıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_335" id="167r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw, und uns yeczunden ein gütlich steen ist,
                        das <add>nu</add> auf <app><note><q type="date">sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1411</note></app> awsgeet,
                            <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersam
                                <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> czemal fleisziklich, daz ir es
                        durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tün und
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> gemüwet sein wollet und besehen, ob ir
                        mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw <expan>awsgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht,
                        daz das etlich czeite hinfür erlengt würd. Und wöllet ew das
                                <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> sein. Als etc. und das in
                                <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
